quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,85,"Annaguna (Alle ah Ogaal iyo Awood ahaan iyo malaa’igtayada) idiinka dhownahay, laakiinse aydaan arkayn."
  56,86,"Haddaad tihiin kuwo aan la soo bixineyn oo la xisaabineyn (Aakhirada)."
  56,87,"Maxaad Ugu soo celin (weydeen) nafta (jirkeedii) haddaad run sheegeysaan?"
  67,25,"Waxay odhan: Waa goorma waqtiga gooddigani la fulin haddaad run sheegi?"
  67,26,"Dheh: Alle baa Og (waqtigay tahay), waxaanse ahay anigu dige cad."
  67,27,"Markayse arkaan (cadaabka Ilaahay) oo ku soo dhow, waxaa xumaan wejiyada gaalada, waxaana lagu odhan: Waa kan waxaad u yeedhan jirteen (in la idiin soo dedejiyo oo cadaab ah)."
  68,19,"Markaasaa waxaa uga yimid amar (dab) xagga Rabbigaa habeennimadii (oo beertii gubatay) intay hurdeen."
  68,20,"Markaasay noqotay sida xaabo madoobaatay oo la shafay."
  68,21,"Waxay isu dhawaaqeen subaxnimadii,"
  69,16,"Samadu Maalintaa u kala dillaaci gaballo, marka waxay ahaan mid jilicsan."
  69,17,"Malaa’igtu waxay ahaan agagaar- keeda, waxaana ku xambaari Carshiga Rabbigaa korkooda Maalintaas siddeed (saf oo malaa'g ah)."
  69,18,"Maalintaas waa la idin soo bandhigi, ma jirto sir aad leedihiin oo qarsoonaan."
  70,10,"Saaxiib uusan saaxiib kale wax weydiineyn."
  70,11,"Wayse is arkayaan, denbiilahu wuxuu jeclaan inuu isaga furto Maalintaasi (Qiyaamada) cadaabka ilmahiisa."
  70,12,"Iyo xaaskiisa iyo walaalki."
  71,7,"Mar kastoo aan u yeedhana si aad ugu denbi dhaafto, waxay yeelaan farahooda dhegahooda, iskuna dadaan maryahooda{2}, oo madax adaygaan, wayna is kibriyaan iskibrin.",1:[. Iyagoo diidaya inay fiirshaan ama dhageystaan Xaqa.],2:[]
  71,8,"Haddana waxaan ugu baaqay (Towxiidka oo uga digay shirkiga) si cod kore ah."
  71,9,"Waxaan ula hadlay si kore, si hoosana waan ula hadlay oo wax ugu sheegay{2}.",1:[. Wuxuu Nuux c.s. la soo maray ku baaqiisa Islaamka heerar iyo xaalado kala duwan:],2:[]
  72,4,"Wuxuu ahaa kan maan gaabka ahi{2} ee dhexdeenna ah mid ka sheega hadallo xadgudub ah aan habbooneyn Alle.",1:[. Ibliis. Waxaa sidoo kale lagu fasiri karaa wadar ahaan, markaas waa in la yidhaahdo: “iyo in kuweenna maangaabka ahi ee naga mid ah”.],2:[]
  72,5,"Waxaan u malaynaynay inaysan dadka iyo jinkaba ka been sheegin Alle."
  72,6,"Waxay rag ku jira dadka magan galayeen rag ku jira jinka, markaasay u kordhiyeen dhib iyo culeys (denbi)."
